text: Yvette Renee Wilson (March 6, 1964 - June 14, 2012) was an American comedian and actress. She was best known for her role as Andell Wilkerson in Moesha and its spinoff The Parkers. Wilson was born on March 6, 1964 in Los Angeles, California. She studied at San Jose State Univeristy.
